block section_movement_overview
  | Movement in Valorant is relatively different from other FPS games
  | As most gun fights require you to stand still the bulk of the movement comes in strafing between your shots and how you open into an angle
  | It is important to open in a way to throw your oponent off guard, for example, swing for an extra second to surprise your enemy 
  | It is also important to only open an angle using A or D movement key as your movement inaccuracy resets faster

